{"id":"refiner","term":"Refiner","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>The process of refining metals is referred to by way of illustrations in <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 1:25\">Isa. 1:25</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Jeremiah 6:29\">Jer. 6:29</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Zechariah 13:9\">Zech. 13:9</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Malachi 3:2\">Mal. 3:2</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Malachi 3:3\">3</a>.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Isaiah 1:25","Jeremiah 6:29","Zechariah 13:9","Malachi 3:2","Malachi 3:3"]}